org.bytedeco.bullet.BulletSoftBody

Class btSoftBody

  • java.lang.Object

    AutoCloseable

    @NoOffset
 @Properties(inherit=BulletSoftBody.class)
public class btSoftBody
extends btCollisionObject
    The btSoftBody is an class to simulate cloth and volumetric soft bodies. There is two-way interaction between btSoftBody and btRigidBody/btCollisionObject.
